            <p style="text-align:center;">
              <% if params[:locale]=='en' %>
                <p style="text-align:center;"><b>2015 CONFERENCE IS COMING!</b></p>
                <p>2015 Science and Technology AKSTS conference will  be from 19 to 21 of July 2015.</p>
                <p>Conference will be hold in Moscow or Moscow territory. Conference will be in format CIS - Korea. Soon registration will be opened.</p>
                <p>Sincerely Yours AKSTS</p>
              <% else %>
